SUMMARY:**10 AM** Friday Walk to and from Council Crest from Hillsdale Library 
DESCRIPTION:Portland City Trail Walking Group\nAdapted from “Portland Stair Walks” by Laura O. Foster: Hilly loop walk up to Council Crest Park and back from the Hillsdale Library in SW Portland. About 550' elevation over 5 miles. Neighborhood streets\, trails in a mini-forest\, and stairs.
