SUMMARY:**10 AM** Portland SW Hills Stairway to Heaven(ly) Goose Hollow Walk
DESCRIPTION:Portland City Trail Walking Group\n*Adapted from the 2010 edition of "Portland Stair Walks" by Laura O.Foster*\n\nIncredible 3.4 miles\, 328 ascending and 300+ descending stairs. Optional lunch at Goose Hollow Inn after the walk.\nExcellent views and architecture of the neighborhood above and around the PSU campus.\nYou might want to bring water…you’ll sweat or glow.\nLimited parking near the start on SW 20th Ave and SW Howards Way south of Jefferson Street.\n\\*\\*Additonal on-street parking near 1952 SW Market Street in the neighborhood above the starting point.\\*\\*\n\n**Meetup start point is uphill on SW 20th Ave south of SW Howards Way**
